data.description:
BACK ON MARKET -- Buyer's financing fell through -- NO fault of the Sellers!!!
Check out this gorgeous BA home in BA schools that has three large, downstairs bedrooms with a huge bedroom upstairs that can also be used as a flex space; lots of storage throughout (linen closets, 2 floored attic spaces, large closet with the upstairs bonus area as well); come cool off in the newly resurfaced saltwater pool! adjacent to the new 55 acre Elam Park being constructed as well as the Aspen Ridge Shopping Center less than a mile away; relaxing sunroom with flooring replaced in 2019; the hallway bathroom has fresh paint and tiled floor with a new toilet in 2022; hot water heater installed 2022 with a new downstairs HVAC system installed in 2019; in addition to the pool you'll love the custom-built pergola with all cedar construction and Trex all-weather flooring for low maintenance built in 2017; curl up to a gas or wood-burning fireplace with family and friends; also includes a humidifier for the entire home; French drains included for proper backyard draining; close to major highways and retail for easy living! The pool decking has just been resurfaced as well. If you want a large, nice home with a gorgeous gunite pool already installed so you don't have to dig up your yard and mess up the lawn from all the heavy machinery... THIS IS IT!!!
